| CONN-HQ-002   | FW-HQ1       | port2     | SW-HQ-L3-1   | Gi1/0/1  | Ethernet   | LAN Uplink         |
| CONN-HQ-003   | FW-HQ2       | port1     | RTR-HQ2      | Gi0/0    | Ethernet   | WAN Uplink         |
| CONN-HQ-004   | FW-HQ2       | port2     | SW-HQ-L3-2   | Gi1/0/1  | Ethernet   | LAN Uplink         |
| CONN-HQ-005   | FW-HQ1       | port3     | FW-HQ2       | port3    | Ethernet   | HA Heartbeat       |
| CONN-HQ-006   | RTR-HQ1      | Gi0/1     | RTR-HQ2      | Gi0/1    | Ethernet   | Router Redundancy  |
| CONN-HQ-007   | SW-HQ-L3-1   | Gi1/0/24  | SW-HQ-L3-2   | Gi1/0/24 | Ethernet   | Switch Stack       |
| CONN-HQ-008   | SW-HQ-L3-1   | Gi1/0/10  | SW-HQ-L2-1   | Gi1/0/1  | Ethernet   | To Access Layer    |
| CONN-HQ-009   | SW-HQ-L3-2   | Gi1/0/10  | SW-HQ-L2-2   | Gi1/0/1  | Ethernet   | To Access Layer    |

## IP Addressing Scheme

### HQ Subnets

| Subnet Name | Network CIDR    | Gateway      | VLAN ID | Purpose                  |
|-------------|-----------------|--------------|---------|--------------------------|
| SERVERS     | 10.10.10.0/24   | 10.10.10.1   | 10      | Core Banking Servers     |
| USERS       | 10.10.20.0/24   | 10.10.20.1   | 20      | HQ Staff Workstations    |

### Branch Subnets

| Branch      | Network CIDR    | Gateway      | VLAN ID | Purpose        |
|-------------|-----------------|--------------|---------|----------------|
| BR1         | 10.20.10.0/24   | 10.20.10.1   | 10      | Branch Users   |
| BR2         | 10.30.10.0/24   | 10.30.10.1   | 10      | Branch Users   |
| BR3         | 10.40.10.0/24   | 10.40.10.1   | 10      | Branch Users   |
| BR4         | 10.50.10.0/24   | 10.50.10.1   | 10      | Branch Users   |

