| **HQ**       | 1        | DHCP Server         | 10.10.10.40   | IP Management       |
| **HQ**       | 1        | AAA Server          | 10.10.10.50   | Authentication      |
| **HQ**       | 1        | Syslog Server       | 10.10.10.60   | Logging             |
| **Each Branch**| 2      | Teller Workstations | .100-150      | Banking Operations  |
| **Each Branch**| 1      | Customer Service PC | .151-160      | Customer Support    |
| **Each Branch**| 1      | ATM Simulator       | .161-170      | ATM Interface       |

