## Security Zones

| Zone Name    | Security Level | Devices                  | Description               |
|--------------|---------------|--------------------------|---------------------------|
| Untrust      | 0             | Internet-facing interfaces | External WAN Connections  |
| Trust        | 100           | Internal user networks   | Trusted Internal Zone     |
| DMZ          | 50            | Public servers           | Demilitarized Zone        |
| Management   | 200           | Network infrastructure   | Management Interfaces     |

## High Availability Configuration

| Parameter          | Primary FW-HQ1 | Secondary FW-HQ2 |
|--------------------|----------------|------------------|
| HA Mode            | Active         | Passive          |
| Priority           | 200            | 150              |
| Monitor Interfaces | port1, port2   | port1, port2     |
| Failover Time      | < 5 seconds    | < 5 seconds      |

